</li><li> <em><a class="urllink" href="https://www.fimfiction.net/story/197974/sweetie-belle-blackjack-dealer-yay">Sweetie Belle: Blackjack Dealer. Yay!<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a></em>: Upon learning Sweetie Belle got a job at a casino, Rarity storms into the owner's office and tears him a new one, until he offers that family of employees get half off on the buffet on Fridays, causing her to pull a 180.
<div class="indent"><strong>Rarity:</strong> I don&#146;t know what it is you think you&#146;re doing, but Sweetie Belle is my sister! You are going to abandon whatever sick, twisted plan you have for her or I will shove my hoof so far up your plot that you will need a royal decree from Celestia herself to remove it! I will burn this place to ashes and then I will burn those ashes! I WILL BUCK YOU UP! <br><strong>Royal Flush:</strong> Umm employee families get half off our buffet on Fridays? <br><strong>Rarity:</strong> Oh, well that sounds lovely. Never mind then. Have fun Sweetie.
