<ul><li> The <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FlyingDutchman" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FlyingDutchman">Flying Dutchman</a> offered some pocket change ("<em>62 cents!</em>") to <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Greed" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Greed">Mr. Krabs</a> if he sold SpongeBob's soul to him. Mr. Krabs sold SpongeBob's soul for the pocket change. Even <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EvenEvilHasStandards" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/EvenEvilHasStandards">Squidward</a></em>, who absolutely hates SpongeBob, called him out on it. A <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Beat" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Beat">Beat</a> goes by... and cue Mr. Krabs' <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OhCrap" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OhCrap">Oh, Crap!</a>/<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MyGodWhatHaveIDone" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MyGodWhatHaveIDone">My God, What Have I Done?</a> face.
</li><li> In <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheSpongeBobSquarePantsMovie" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheSpongeBobSquarePantsMovie">The SpongeBob SquarePants Movie</a></em>, SpongeBob attempts to bribe Dennis with "Goober Dollers". He's unimpressed.
